description:
REV Token is the primary money to serve on the margin trading platform.
REV Token was built on ERC-20 Ethereum, the most outstanding blockchain in existence and a major currency that will serve as a means of service on the margin trading platform through to digital contracts called smart trade, enable margin trading as well as general trading.
It's compatible with Ethereum blockchain-based tokens and also be used in conjunction with many distribution platforms.
name: REV Project
